+sdp/logs/Lead_T-021_20260425T183959Zc_1777175888.log:3264:| `my-claw/tools/senseweave/sampler_buffers.py` | `BufferLoader` — an LRU-bounded scsynth buffer pool. Issues `/b_alloc` and `/b_allocRead` over OSC, evicts the least-recently-used buffer through `on_sampler_free()` when capacity is reached, and returns a stable `bufnum` to the dispatcher. |
